1. "*Slušajte* pažljivo!", (Listen carefully!)
2. "Oni su ti *slušali* iz godine u godinu.", (They had been listening to you year after year.)
3. "*Slušala* sam ga dugo.", (I had been listening to him for a long time.)
4. "*Slušajući* njene reči, shvatio sam šta želi da kaže.", (Listening to her words, I understood what she wanted to say.)
5. "Ona *sluša* njene instrukcije.", (She listens to her instructions.)